---
layout: layouts/base.njk
---
<div class="portal-wrap reader-shell guide-reader-shell" data-pagefind-body>
  <a class="reader-content-skip" href="#lesson-content">跳过目录，进入学习指南正文</a>
  {% include "partials/book-outline.njk" %}

  <article class="reader-content guide-content" id="lesson-content" tabindex="-1" aria-labelledby="guide-title">
    <header class="guide-heading">
      <p class="eyebrow">第一次来 · 从这里开始</p>
      <h1 id="guide-title">{{ title }}</h1>
      <p class="lead">{{ description }}</p>
      <div class="guide-heading-actions">
        <a class="button button-primary" href="{{ '/learn/math/diagnostic.html' | siteUrl }}">开始不打分的诊断</a>
        <a class="button button-quiet" href="{{ '/' | siteUrl }}#start-here">回到三条起步路线</a>
      </div>
    </header>

    <div class="course-prose" data-course-prose>
      {{ content | safe }}

      <section class="guide-finish" aria-labelledby="guide-finish-title">
        <p class="section-kicker">今天只做一件事</p>
        <h2 id="guide-finish-title">不知道选哪门，就从不打分的诊断开始</h2>
        <p>会做的写过程，不会的写“不知道”。完成后只选一个最小缺口补，不要一次打开很多课程。</p>
        <a class="button button-primary" href="{{ '/learn/math/diagnostic.html' | siteUrl }}">带我开始第一步</a>
      </section>
    </div>
  </article>
  {% include "partials/page-outline.njk" %}
</div>
